{"tid":1096423,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日畀女朋友傷害咗自尊","createTime":"2019-04-07T16:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T10:23:19.000Z","uid":223511,"like":31,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a364ffac3b8cf8e1d32bdd5006754f617e9e7713","tid":1096423,"uid":223511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:39:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日同女朋友行街嗰時，唔記得做乜，講咗去碌鳩嘅問題到。<br />\n<br />\n佢：算罷啦你，咁短。<br />\n我：收皮，邊撚到短？<br />\n佢：下話？唔講啦，費事傷你自尊心。<br />\n<br />\n嗰時我都有小小嬲，到咗夜晚返咗屋企，同佢wts傾計講我生倒刺<br />\n<br />\n佢：剪咗佢<br />\n我：（影隻手）太短剪唔到<br />\n佢：似你🥴<br />\n我：邊撚到似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢：細🥴🤪<br />\n<br />\n然後我就嬲撚咗<br />\n<br />\n利申：16cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都對自己碌鳩都幾有自信，16cm可能唔算係好長，但起碼高過香港個mean幾多 。<br />\n<br />\n平時佢笑尻我其他嘢都冇乜所謂，但係有啲嘢係唔講得笑。就算佢真係覺得16cm短，都唔係咁樣笑尻自己男朋友，都畀返啲尊重呀，就好似佢平到仆街我都冇笑過佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持樓主，有啲嘢係唔可以拎嚟講笑，要畀返啲尊重<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收皮啦樓主，講下笑有乜問題"},{"pid":"07327c425e70bb43e00f714f7f82a9fbaa375a18","tid":1096423,"uid":172244,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed689c063ce024fda58a3db89a222e97cd030a6","tid":1096423,"uid":97604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:41:14.000Z","msg":"你蠢啦<br />\n唔識同你條女講執返劑睇吓lor"},{"pid":"a88f7eed957e4d16aaaaba3a993ed85503e566d8","tid":1096423,"uid":38738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:49:25.000Z","msg":"係唔係佢比你長？"},{"pid":"b496b1e1395f6c185ec170b176a309ef67bd06ca","tid":1096423,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"佢ex好長好硬?"},{"pid":"ac40d7fe3b9270e8c55f7174f03c10d675f528dd","tid":1096423,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"